</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">Hololive英语-Promise-订阅人数首次突破100万</h3><p>无名无名所属的 Hololive English 的《Promise》（原 Council &amp; Project:HOPE）以艺人频道的订阅人数在出道后立即大幅减少的现象以及《九十九草无名》而闻名。除了先生毕业之外，公司也面临着困难，一些其他公司和团体的人才表示， <em>“理事会的表现没有达到他们的预期</em>。” </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="GUIUrVqqa7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-hololive-english-youtube-subscribers-of-5-new-talents-decreased-but-the-cause-is-unknown/">VTuber团体Hololive英语5位新秀频道订阅数减少，原因不明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber 团体 Hololive 英语频道 5 名新人订阅人数减少，原因不明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-hololive-english-youtube-subscribers-of-5-new-talents-decreased-but-the-cause-is-unknown/embed/#?secret=jHWkVZFvaq#?secret=GUIUrVqqa7" data-secret="GUIUrVqqa7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="DmKLnZy977"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/the-line-of-sight-to-hololive-production-can-be-seen-from-the-interesting-exchanges-of-nijisanji-group-nijisanji-en-discord/">着眼于 Hololive Production 关于 Nijisanji “NIJISANJI EN” 的有趣交流 Discord</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“看 Hololive 制作：关于 Nijisanji “NIJISANJI EN”Discord 的有趣交流” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/the-line-of-sight-to-hololive-production-can-be-seen-from-the-interesting-exchanges-of-nijisanji-group-nijisanji-en-discord/embed/#?secret=4bTCjLrV6V#?secret=DmKLnZy977" data-secret="DmKLnZy977" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figu