jIjc3YsW#?secret=zQSLWZjdDS" data-secret="zQSLWZjdDS" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/thai-vtuber-agency-virtual-zeven-debuts-new-talents-summ3r-and-wint3r-from-project-sw33th34rt/">泰国VTuber办公室Virtual Zeven“PRØJECT SW33TH34RT”的新人“SUMM3R”和“WINT3R”</a>首次亮相于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; https://p2y.jp/thai-vtuber-agency-virtual-zeven-debuts-new-talents-summ3r-and-wint3r-from-project-sw33th34rt/feed/ 0 112752
